com.att.research.xacmlatt.pdp.std

Class StdEvaluationContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.att.research.xacmlatt.pdp.std.StdEvaluationContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PIPFinder, TraceEngine, EvaluationContext

    public class StdEvaluationContext
extends java.lang.Object
implements EvaluationContext
    StdEvaluationContext implements the EvaluationContext interface using default factories to load the XACML policies, and get the PIP engines.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.1 $
    Author:
    car
